Name: Xel'Naga Precursor
Description: Basic worker unit. Can gather resources and warp in Xel'Naga structures.**Can attack ground units**

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target area or follow the target unit. Moving units will not engage enemies.
Root.Name: Move

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to cancel all orders and stop moving.
Root.Name: Stop

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to stay where they are and attack enemies that are within range. Units will neither chase down enemies nor move to engage.
Root.Name: Hold Position

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target point, fighting nearby enemies along the way. Targeting a unit with the Attack command orders that it be attacked until it is destroyed.
Root.Name: Attack

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to patrol between their current position and the target area. Units will attack enemies and move to engage nearby enemies.
Root.Name: Patrol

Root.Tooltip: Orders Probe to gather resources from a selected Mineral Field or Vespene Geyser.
Root.Name: Gather

Root.Tooltip: Returns the carried resources to the nearest drop-off point.
Root.Name: Return Cargo

Root.Tooltip: Orders the unit to apply your currently selected spray to the terrain at the target location.
Root.Name: Spray

PBl1.Tooltip:
Primary structure. Can receive gathered resources. Can use the Chrono Boost ability. Can Warp in Ancient Assimilators.

Enables:
- Xel'Naga Precursor
PBl1.Name: Warp in Ancient Nexus

PBl1.Tooltip:
Builds basic Protoss and Xel'Naga ground units.

Enables:
- Xel'Naga Ambushers
PBl1.Name: Warp In Xel'Naga Passageway

PBl1.Tooltip:
Contains weapon and armor upgrades for Xel'Naga air units.

Enables:
- Xel'Naga Shieldguards at the Xel'Naga Passageway
- Xel'Naga Ambushers at the Xel'Naga Passageway
- Xel'Naga Glaives at the Xel'Naga Passageway
PBl1.Name: Warp In Xel'Naga Core

PBl1.Tooltip:
Primary defensive structure. Can project itself onto the battlefield. Can use Shade Barrier to absorb damage.**Can attack ground and air units**
Detector
PBl1.Name: Warp In Tesseract Cannon

PBl1.Tooltip: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
PBl1.Name: Cancel

PBl1.Tooltip:
Contains weapon and armor upgrades for Xel'Naga ground units and shield upgrades for all Protoss units and structures.

Enables:
- Tesseract Cannon from Xel'Naga Precursor- Tesseract Battery from Xel'Naga Precursor- Tesseract Monolith from Xel'Naga Precursor
PBl1.Name: Warp In Xel'Naga Forge

PBl1.Tooltip:
Deploys a Tesseract Monolith at the target location. Tesseract Monoliths can stun enemies, project themselves, and protect themselves from damage.**Can attack ground and air units**
Detector
PBl1.Name: Warp In Tesseract Monolith

PBl1.Tooltip: Restores life and shields to nearby friendly units and structures.
PBl1.Name: Warp in Tesseract Battery

PBl2.Tooltip:
Builds Xel'Naga robotic constructs.

Enables:
- Xel'Naga Enforcers
- Xel'Naga Void Arrays
- Xel'Naga Watchers
PBl2.Name: Warp In Constructs Facility

PBl2.Tooltip:
Contains Artifact upgrades for Void Templar.

Enables:
- Void Templar at the Xel'Naga Passageway
PBl2.Name: Warp In Void Shrine

PBl2.Tooltip:
Contains Artifact upgrades for Xel'Naga Enforcers, Xel'Naga Void Arrays, and Xel'Naga Watchers.

Enables:
- Xel'Naga Abrogators at the Constructs Facility
PBl2.Name: Warp In Constructs Bay

PBl2.Tooltip: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
PBl2.Name: Cancel
